<refsect1 id="TotemVideoList.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
<link linkend="TotemVideoList"><type>TotemVideoList</type></link> is a <link linkend="GtkTreeView"><type>GtkTreeView</type></link> designed for listing videos by their thumbnails using <link linkend="TotemCellRendererVideo"><type>TotemCellRendererVideo</type></link>.
It supports tooltips, loading the videos by activating tree view rows, and <link linkend="GtkUIManager"><type>GtkUIManager</type></link> actions in the popup menu.</para>
<para>
</para>
</refsect1>

